parameters:
\n<Dodon>Damn it! What's going on all of a sudden!! Hey! Rui! It's an
attack! Kill the monsters!!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Rui!? Not looking, huh?! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You too, protect the town!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Ones!? Not looking, huh?! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You too, protect the town!

\n<Succubus>"Slurp♥ Slurrrrp♥ Are you going to die already? That's too
quick-. Boring♥ Maybe I should cast a healing spell-."

\n<Succubus>"Slurp♥ Slurrrrp♥ This one's so tasty♥ Even though you're
quick to cum♥"
1テラ普通2

\n<???>What a filthy town. Hehe♥ I don't dislike places like this,
though it's not quite fitting for me.
1ラティエ普通2

\n<Latier>Lady Terra, you look beautiful as always. The contrast with
this town makes you shine even brighter♥ Like a goddess.

\n<Succubus A>Lady Terra! Lady Terra! Why would you bother coming to a
place like this?
\n<Succubus B>Can we drain all the humans in this town dry today?
1メグナ困惑

\n<Megna>...(Is this succubus Terra...? Just being near her makes it
hard to breathe... Scary!!)
1シェイカ怒り

\n<Sheika>Are you seriously planning to destroy this town? Just leave
the box alone...
1バーリィ困惑

\n<Barley>...(I wonder if all the audience members will die too. Well,
it doesn't matter.)
1テラ笑い

\n<Terra>Don't you feel it? An immense malice. I've come to collect
it.
1テラ普通2

\n<Terra>Whether the town is destroyed or not is irrelevant. It's a
trivial matter.
\n<Monster>Guaaaaaaahhhhh!!!

\n<Annie>Rui! The town's in chaos! We've evacuated everyone who can't
fight! But there are monsters in the residential area
too...! Damn it! Why is this happening all of a sudden!!
\n<Monster>Guaaaaaaahhhhh!!!
1ラドロP驚き

\n<Radro>Why are monsters suddenly...! I'll definitely protect the
children here! Rui, go around the town! Help everyone...!
1ラドロP絶

\n<Radro>But don't do anything reckless...! If something happens to
Rui... I...! If you think it's dangerous, escape!

\n<Female>You're an adventurer, right? Please, I'm counting on you to
protect the town. Defeat the monsters for us.

\n<Female>Leave this place to me. Even if I become a corpse, I'll
block the door. Besides, my reliable partner is also
starving for action!
\n<Dirty Dog>Grrrrrrr...!

\n<Lintei>Ugh...! I'm weak against these sudden attacks! I'm the type
who needs to prepare thoroughly!

\n<Lintei>But I can't afford to lose! Lynx, Cunes... lend me your
strength...!
\n<Monster>Kyuaaaaaaah!!
There's no response. It seems they've already passed away.
\n<Rakura>Tch! Take this! Lightning Spear!
\n<Rakura>Why won't you die already! You monster...!
\n<Monster>Guaaaaaaahhhhh!!!

\n<Siebel>I can fight too, you know! Idiot, idiot, idiot! Get out of
here!!
\n<Siebel>Ha! I did it! Serves you right! Loser, loser!
\n<Siebel>Seconds!?
\n<Monster>Kyuaaaaaaaaah!!

\n<Soldier>No, you can't pass! I cannot allow you through here! This is
an order! If you don't leave, I'll have no choice but to cut
you down!
\n<Soldier>(I'm sorry... Even I... truly don't want to do this...)

\n<Tanuki Beastman>Hmm, oh! A cat beastperson. I'm currently avoiding danger by
disguising myself as trash. Pretty smart, huh?

\n<Tanuki Beastman>Huh? I'm not disguised? You're kidding... Oh, it's true.
Well, whatever. When it's time to die, I'll die.

\n<Old Man>Young Lady! Thank goodness...! I'm so relieved you're
safe...!!
\n<Old Man>What!? The young master is missing!? That can't be...!

\n<Old Man>Young Master! Thank goodness...! I'm so relieved you're
safe...!!

\n<Old Man>What!? The young lady is nowhere to be seen...!? That can't
be...!

\n<Old Man>Perhaps they noticed the approach of the monsters early on.
If that's the case, they might be fighting to the south.

\n<Old Man>When I jumped down from the noble district, I injured my
leg... I'm sorry. If only I had secured a lodging here...

\n<Rui>Thanks, old man. You go hide somewhere safe now! Leave the
rest to me.

\n<Rui>Thank you! Old man! Now please evacuate to a safe place! I
will definitely find Ones...!
C
\n<Old Man>Please take care. But don't push yourself too hard...

\n<Old Man>I will evacuate the injured and those who have fallen behind
to the orphanage.

\n<Old Man>The monsters are attacking from the south! Please take care
of the young master...! But do not overexert yourself!
Heal...!

\n<Old Man>The monsters are attacking from the south! Please take care
